學科別＞人文學＞語言文學



中文摘要
本論文以 1980-2008 其間台灣的飲食散文文本為研究對象。先架構飲食散文書寫史，再析論其藝術表現，最後呈現其文化意涵。  首先探討台灣現當代飲食散文在八○年代後大為風行的原因。分析興起背景為受中國傳統典籍飲食書寫影響、移民社會飲食現象多元、經濟發展帶來消費與旅行風氣以及媒體出版業推波助瀾。本論文認為，八○年代之後崛起的飲食散文可依特色分為三階段：1980-1987 為第一階段，特徵是表現對中國大陸的鄉愁。隨著解嚴進入第二階段，1988-1998 十年之間，結合旅行的飲食散文及結合自然的飲食散文都已出現，同時想像的家鄉味隨開放探親而幻滅，西方的飲食文化帶來衝擊，飲食散文開始醞釀多元的面貌。1999-2008 為第三階段，在此期間飲食散文蔚為風尚，建立各種風格與模式，至今仍不斷推陳出新。  台灣當代飲食散文的藝術表現，主要為詳盡的敘事、意有所指的詠物及揉合歷史表現文化的議論。而考察其內容則可發現飲食散文寓寄情感、呈現社會變遷軌跡，同時透顯女性性別意識，並與消費及慾望不斷相互對話，此為當代飲食散文所主要傳達之文化意涵。  綜上所述，證成當代飲食散文寫作是散文中一重要且有價值之次文類。


英文摘要
The prose of diet, issued in Taiwan between 1980 and 2008, were studied in this essay. First the history of diet prose was featured; then the artistic achievement was analyzed, finally, the cultural value was performed. Analysis on the historical background of the reasons why Taiwan modern diet prose grew to be popular in 1980's was first discussed, and it showed, influence from diet writing in Chinese classics, multi-culture of the immigration society, travel atmosphere and consumer culture brought which along with the economical growth , and incitation by media and the publication. It was concluded in this essay that, the diet prose arose after 1980's could be observed in three phases: the first phase was from 1980 till 1987, with characteristic of the homesickness to Mainland China. The second phase was between 1988 and 1998, came together with the lifting of martial law. The diet prose based on travel experience or telling the beauty of Nature started to emerge. At the same time, the hometown taste in imagination vaporized as homecoming to China became true. The western foods impacted Taiwan greatly, and fostered the diverse aspects of diet prose. The third phase existed since 1999 till 2008, diet prose flourished during this period of time, various styles and structures were built, and have been breeding new creations. The artistic performance of Taiwan modern diet prose mainly focused on detailing statement, delivering implications behind the chanted things, and criticizing via cultural and historical elements. It was found in reviewing the diet prose that, they voiced sentiments, presented the track of society migration, also revealed women’s recognition on gender role, and kept mutually influencing fashion and desires. This is the major cultural value delivered through modern diet prose. It can be concluded according to the above arguments that, the works of modern diet prose is an essential and valuable sub-genre of prose.


